Building Radx using configure
-----------------------------

A typical build sequence is as follows:

  setenv CPPFLAGS "-I/usr/local/netcdf4/include"
  setenv CFLAGS "-O2"
  configure --prefix=/tmp/radx
  make
  make install

For a non-optimized compile, use:

  setenv CFLAGS "-g"





